itemDescription: Ugandan/British Entrepreneur, Innovator and Thought Leader

wikipedia_page.main: Nataliey Bitature (born in 1989), is a Ugandan entrepreneur and executive, currently serving as Chief of Staff at The Simba Group. Bitature was named in the Forbes 30 Under 30 in 2015 and is the daughter of Patrick Bitature, one of the richest people in Uganda.
